### Add Span event generation to trace end method

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Span event generation has been added to the trace 'end' method.  This enables the creation of span events when a trace completes.

```javascript
trace.end(); // Now generates Span events
```

