### Recommended AI Monitoring Settings

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

These settings are recommended for a full AI Monitoring experience, including increased sample storage for span events and custom insights, and ensuring distributed tracing is enabled. These configurations enhance the observability of AI interactions.

```json
{
  "span_events": {
    "max_samples_stored": 10000
  },
  "custom_insights_events": {
    "max_samples_stored": 100000
  },
  "distributed_tracing": {
    "enabled": true
  }
}
```

